MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is to load data from table STG_HAA_INVENTORY to table BI_INVENTORY
MAPPING.NAME: m_PAC_BI_INV_LOAD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Union onhand and intransit data
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: UN_ONHAND_INTRANSIT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LOOKUP ON ITEM TABLE FOR getting min ITEM_ID FOR STEP2
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STEP2_ITEM_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, NVL(TRIM(ITEM.STYLE_NUM),'') as STYLE_NUM, NVL(TRIM(ITEM.COLOR_CODE),'') as COLOR_CODE, NVL(TRIM(ITEM.SIZE_CODE),'') as SIZE_CODE, NVL(TRIM(ITEM.CUP_SIZE),'') as CUP_SIZE FROM ITEM WHERE ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP='haa' GROUP BY NVL(TRIM(ITEM.STYLE_NUM),''), NVL(TRIM(ITEM.COLOR_CODE),''), NVL(TRIM(ITEM.SIZE_CODE),''), NVL(TRIM(ITEM.CUP_SIZE),''), ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE_NUM AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR_CODE AND SIZE_CODE = I_SIZE_CODE AND CUP_SIZE = I_CUP_SIZE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup ITEM_ID based on SKU
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STEP1_ITEM_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM_ID) AS ITEM_ID, TRIM(SKU) AS SKU FROM ITEM B WHERE UPPER(DIVISION_GROUP) = 'HAA' GROUP BY TRIM(SKU)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on table Reference to get desc_1 as STYLE_NUM
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_REFERENCE_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT min(Reference.Desc_1) as Desc_1, 'DUMMY' as DUMMY FROM Reference WITH (NOLOCK) where Reference_key='HAADefaultStyle' and Reference_subkey_seq=0

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup ITEM_ID from ITEM
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STEP3_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, ITEM.STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='hbi' GROUP BY STYLE_NUM

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_FACILITY to get MIN facility_id
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE upper(DIVISION_GROUP)='HAA' GROUP BY FACILITY_CODE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LOOKUP FOR GETTING GARM_PER_PKG_QTY FOR STEP 1 and 2
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ITEM_GARM_PER_PKG_QTY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ITEM.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY as GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID FROM ITEM
